        </item>
        <item>
            <title>马斯克投资飞天车 Model A 试飞，无旋翼设计、售价 230 万仍有逾 3 千人排队</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=model-a-flying-car</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 05:24:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[飞天车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293902</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前网上流传一段美国初创企业 Alef Aeronautics 试飞旗下飞天车 Model A 的影片，显示飞行汽车技术迈向实用化新阶段。据悉 Elon Musk 名下的 SpaceX 曾投资该公司。预计 Model A 最快可在 2025 年开始交付。Alef Aero 期望这项突破能为城市交通带来翻天覆地的变革，为用户提供灵活多变的通勤选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>外媒上传的影片显示，美国初创企业 Alef Aeronautics 成功试飞旗下飞天车 Model A，影片显示，这款由 Tesla 行政总裁 Elon Musk 投资的创新飞行器 Model A 飞行器采用无旋翼垂直起降技术，据报 2025 年开始交付。据悉在充满电的状态下， Model A 可水平飞行 177 公里，在地面上续航力可达 322 公里。据《Channel C》报道指，美国联邦航空管理局（FAA）已发出特别适航证书。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293907" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>Alef Aero Model A 车体采用碳纤维物料制成，有效减轻重量并提升结构强度。Model A 可容纳两名乘客，具备垂直升降及水平飞行功能。车体旋转时可由地面驾驶模式无缝切换至飞行模式，成功破解传统飞天车机翼占用空间的技术难题。Alef Aero 希望 Model A 能纾缓城市挤塞问题，特别适合短途通勤及地面驾驶结合的日常应用场景，为用户出行提供「上天下地」的双重选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/alefaeronauticsunvei-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a></p><p>Model A 售价约 30 万美元（约港币 233.24 万元），目前已有逾 3,000 人预订，预计于 2025 年正式投产。Alef Aero 行政总裁 Jim Dukhovny 指，Model A 能在交通高峰时解决拥堵问题，更可在紧急情况下提供另类逃生途径。他补充，公司正积极开发价格更亲民的版本，希望普及飞天车技术，使更多人享受其带来的便捷与创新。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_24890"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lCmfrCJBvSk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片、资料来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@NEWS9LIVE">NEWS9 Live@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E8%B5%B7%E9%99%8D-%E7%84%A1%E6%97%8B%E7%BF%BC-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E5%8F%83%E6%8A%95-%E9%A3%9B%E5%A4%A9%E8%BB%8A-%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-072002250.html">anue</a>、<a href="https://businessfocus.io/article/305207/%E9%A3%9B%E5%A4%A9%E8%BB%8A-alef-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B">business focus</a>、<a href="https://channelchk.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8AModel-A%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E9%80%BE30%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%B7%B2%E6%8E%A53%E5%8D%83%E5%A4%9A%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE">Channel C</a>、<a href="https://www.startupselfie.net/2025/02/21/alef-aeronautics-drivable-flying-car-first-flight/">Startup selfie</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/model-a-flying-car/life-tech/auto/">马斯克投资飞天车 Model A 试飞，无旋翼设计、售价 230 万仍有逾 3 千人排队</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
