            <title>日本发明三文鱼除骨机   AI 判断骨头位置，再用机械臂除骨取代人手</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/salmon-bone/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=salmon-bone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/24/salmon-bone/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 10:47:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[饮食]]>
            </category>
